Winnie Madikizela-MandelaWinnie Madikizela-Mandela, the mother of the nation, turned 80 yesterday, looking good. Her 80th birthday appearance (see picture) has attracted plastic surgery rumours. This is mainly due to her face looking drastically different she looks much younger than her celebrated years. Her daughter, Zindzi Mandela, in responding to the rumours took to Twitter to comment. Pure African beauty. No fillers or injections involved, she tweeted. We join the people of South Africa in wishing Mam Winnie a happy birthday. Agencies/HR. (Picture by Elizabeth Idowu)